<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Stetzman und Marquart Waltman</head><p>Der Rat teilt das Gerücht von der Gefangennahme des Hiltpolt Zinner, Bürger zu Nürnberg, durch Hiltpolt von Fraunberg mit und bittet um Bestätigung und Fürsprache bei Herzog Stephan III. von Bayern-Ingolstadt wegen dessen Freilassung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_187" id="92r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_187_r1l17">Hanſen Stecʒman vnd <expan>M<ex>arka</ex>r<ex>t</ex></expan> VValtman </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_187_r1l18">Wir <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ew vviſſen / daʒ vns geſagt ıſt worden / vvie daʒ her Hılpolt <expan>frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_187_r1l19"><expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / den Hıltpolt Cʒiner <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / Davon ſo laſt nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_187_r1l20">Jr ervaret ew darvmb / vnd wer es daʒ dem alſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> / ſo bringt das an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_187_r1l21"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Hercʒog Stephan / vnd beſeht ob er ledig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de<ex>n</ex></expan> möht / wer <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_187_r1l22">ye niht ledig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möcht / So 
<add><ab facs="#facs_187_line_1575890192958_1252">be </ab></add> ſeht doch / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">man Jm tag vnd awſgeb </del> / Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_187_r1l23">Hercʒog Stephan beholffen ſeÿ daʒ Jm tag <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıȷ̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Oc<ex>u</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_187" id="92r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen Steczman und <expan>M<ex>arka</ex>r<ex>t</ex></expan> Waltman </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wissen, daz uns
                                                gesagt ist worden, wie daz her Hilpolt
                                                  <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> süll
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den Hiltpolt Cziner,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, davon so last nicht
                                                ir ervaret ew darumb; und wer es, daz dem also
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, so bringt das an
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog Stephan, und
                                                beseht, ob er ledig
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de<ex>n</ex></expan> möht. Wer
                                                  <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz er ye niht ledig
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> möcht, so
                                                  <add>be</add>seht doch, daz im herczog Stephan
                                                beholffen sey, daz im tag
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>oc<ex>u</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
